\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 <$Scr_Ps::0>As soon as he began reading the announcement, Marcus\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s heart started galloping. The system was practically laying out incentives for groups to hunt one another right alongside the actual objectives. He could only wonder how bad it would get toward the end, when the competition was fiercest. He shot a glance at Cassie, who met his gaze and nodded. <!$Scr_Ps::0>}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\ltrch\loch \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\ltrch\loch {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 <$Scr_Ps::1>You have formed a group with Cassandra Blake!<!$Scr_Ps::1><$Scr_Ps::0>}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\ltrch\loch \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Do you have a Class or a Profession and what is it?\u8221\'94 Cassie asked quickly as she began to look around and see how things were happening as people began scrambling to find groups. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Class, Ma.. Call it Caster for now,\u8221\'94 Marcus changed his mind mid-word as noticed others were close enough to hear. \u8220\'93We can discuss more specifics when there are less ears. You?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Also Class, Striker, if we\u8217\'92re holding cards and waiting for the flop,\u8221\'94 Cassie grinned and threw him another wink. \u8220\'93We need someone to tank and a healer right?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Ideally,\u8221\'94 he agreed with a nod. \u8220\'93Those and one or two more damage dealers and we should be golden.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93You wanna stay under 10?\u8221\'94 she shot him a quick frown. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I figure under 10 will be better rewards, six would be good, five would be better.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93So, we\u8217\'92re playing to win, not just survive?\u8221\'94 The corner of her mouth turned up in an evil smile. \u8220\'93I knew I liked you, Daddy! I\u8217\'92ll go talk to a couple of the beastkin, you see if that dwarf over there is game. He looks tanky and us no-longer-humans need to stick together.\u8221\'94 }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93On it, you find someone you think will fit, bring them in, don\u8217\'92t wait on a second opinion,\u8221\'94 He said as the turned and strode toward the dwarf in question.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Same goes for you, meet back here shortly,\u8221\'94 Cassie turned and flounced off toward the other beastkin she\u8217\'92d talked to.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Marcus sized up the dwarf as he approached them from behihnd. They were maybe 135 cm tall, broad of shoulder and solid looking, wearing what looked like a heavy mail tunic, steel gauntlets, steel spiked boots with a very intimidating axe slung over one shoulder, and a sturdy looking round shield strapped over the other.  As he got within a couple steps of the dwarf, they turned toward him and he almost stumbled. From the back he\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92d been certain it was a male dwarf he was approaching, but no, it most definitely was not.  }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 She had clearly seen him stumble. With a mostly-hidden smirk on her lips, and a twinkle in her eye, the dwarf lady asked, \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Something I can help you with?\u8221\'94 Her voice wasn\u8217\'92t as innuendo laden as Cassie\u8217\'92s had been, but he was pretty sure this was going to be another fine example of him getting teased constantly by a beautiful younger woman. What a world.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93You see the cute fox-girl over there?\u8221\'94 he hooked his thumb towards Cassie, who appeared to be in friendly conversation with a humanoid rabbit and an elf. \u8220\'93We\u8217\'92re putting a group together, since the folks who are still factory default humans seem to be avoiding us custom jobs.\u8221\'94 He smiled, trying and failing to sound casual. \u8220\'93Thought you might want a shot at being on the winning team. You\u8217\'92re what, a Warrior?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Nah, I\u8217\'92m better than any old Warrior, I\u8217\'92m a He\u8230\'85\u8221\'94 her voice trailed off at the expression on Marcus\u8217\'92s face. She followed Marcus\u8217\'92s gaze, spotting several nearby humans who were clearly suspicious of them. Marcus relaxed as she seemed to catch on. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93\u8230\'85a Protector,\u8221\'94 she finished, giving him a quick wink. \u8220\'93What about you, hot stuff?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Caster,\u8221\'94 he lied solemnly, \u8220\'93Cassie over there, the fox-girl, she\u8217\'92s a Striker and is trying to gather us up someone to heal. You interested?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Ooo a hot fox-girl AND a cute dragon-man to ogle? Where do I sign up?\u8221\'94 the dwarf offered Marcus her hand. \u8220\'93Name\u8217\'92s Freya, yes, for real. Blame my mother.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I\u8217\'92m Marcus, welcome to the team, Freya,\u8221\'94 he took her hand and was surprised by how soft and warm it was against his more reptilian skin.<!$Scr_Ps::0>}
