\par\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\ltrch\loch {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 <$Scr_Ps::1>Freya Johansen has joined the group!<!$Scr_Ps::1><$Scr_Ps::0>}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\ltrch\loch \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 A few moments later, two more announcements followed. <!$Scr_Ps::0>}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\ltrch\loch \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\ltrch\loch {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 <$Scr_Ps::1>India Calhoun has joined the group!}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Roberto Guteirrez has joined the group!<!$Scr_Ps::1><$Scr_Ps::0>}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\ltrch\loch \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 It turned out that India was a Rabbitkin \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8216\'91Marksman\u8217\'92, while Roberto was an Elven \u8216\'91Adept.\u8217\'92 They had known each other before the Integration, which made them a solid two-for-one deal. The five of them gathered in a small group, shying away from the rest of the crowd. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Once they were pretty sure they weren\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t being listened to, Marcus started them off, \u8220\'93Okay, big reveal time. I\u8217\'92m pretty sure, based on Cassie and Freya, that almost all of us who stopped being human got better classes than most. So I\u8217\'92ll start the real meet and greet. I\u8217\'92m Marcus, a Dragonkin-Hybrid and a Magus, which is an Uncommon Caster variant.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Oooo, now that is a fancy Class,\u8221\'94 Cassie cooed. \u8220\'93I\u8217\'92m Cassie, not Cassandra, never Cassandra,\u8221\'94 she introduced herself. \u8220\'93I\u8217\'92m an honest to god Kitsune and a Spellblade which is an Uncommon Striker/Caster hybrid.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93And I\u8217\'92m pretty sure poor little weebs all over the Tutorial are weeping over missing the chance to group with you,\u8221\'94 Freya teased, pulling a giggle out of Cassie. \u8220\'93I\u8217\'92m Freya, yes that\u8217\'92s my real name, and you can blame my mother\u8217\'92s love of mythology. As you can see, I\u8217\'92m a Dwarf and I managed to snag Hearthguard which is a rare, dwarf only Warrior variant.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Damn, now I really feel cheated,\u8221\'94 Roberto chimed in. \u8220\'93I roll up with all my slick elf charm and all the chulas are busy flirting with each other or the Dragonkin. No matter how I up my game, I\u8217\'92m always a step behind.\u8221\'94 He was grinning widely and clearly poking fun without malice. \u8220\'93At least I managed to snag a sweet rare adept variant, called Druid.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 India shook her head melodramatically, \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I\u8217\'92m sorry to subject you all to this poor deprived elf\u8230\'85 or was the word depraved?\u8221\'94 He stuck her tongue out at Roberto who muttered something about promises under his breath. \u8220\'93I am India, a Lepori, and the poor elf\u8217\'92s only friend.\u8221\'94 She snickered. \u8220\'93I\u8217\'92m also a Sniper, an uncommon variant of the Marksman.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93So that\u8217\'92s a tank, in the form of the sexy dwarf lady, a melee dps in the form of the sexy fox-lady, a ranged dps in the form of the sexy rabbit lady, some magical smackdown in the form of a scary dragon-dude and this poor elf to keep you all from dying?\u8221\'94 Roberto clarified.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Marcus shook off the moment of surprise brought on by India\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s Class, and nodded at Roberto. \u8220\'93That\u8217\'92s what it looks like, unless somebody has another thought?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Well, we could pick up a couple more guys,\u8221\'94 India suggested. \u8220\'93I mean, I love tacos as much as the next gal, but a little more sausage in the party wouldn\u8217\'92t be a bad thing.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Marcus winced and started to open his mouth but Cassie jumped in ahead of him. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I don\u8217\'92t think so,\u8221\'94 she countered. \u8220\'93See, we don\u8217\'92t just want to survive this Tutorial, we want to win. And since the the score is counted as IP per person, the more people we have the lower our score ends up.\u8221\'94 She looked around, \u8220\'93besides I really did not like the looks I was getting from a lot of these guys. I\u8217\'92m pretty sure this competition is going to get real ugly before its over, and more than a few of these guys around here look like no might not be in their vocabulary unless someone is around to make them stop.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Freya and India instantly lost a good bit of their playfulness and took a closer look at the other people in the room with them. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Yeah,\u8221\'94 Freya agreed with a slow nod. \u8220\'93I can kinda see what you mean. If killing isn\u8217\'92t off limits anymore, what\u8217\'92s a little sexual assault.\u8221\'94 }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 India winced hard, \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I can vouch for Roberto, at least, he\u8217\'92s not that kind of guy. Sure he\u8217\'92ll flirt and joke around with you as long as you\u8217\'92ll put up with him, but when you say stop, he stops.\u8221\'94 She looked questioningly at Marcus. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I\u8217\'92ll vouch for Marcus,\u8221\'94 Cassie said immediately. \u8220\'93I\u8217\'92ve practically thrown myself at him a couple times now and he\u8217\'92s never been anything but a sweet, embarrassed, shy gentleman. Besides, if he ever wants a tumble from me all he needs to do is ask\u8230\'85 or not tell me no.\u8221\'94 }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Freya burst out laughing at the mortified expression on Marcus\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s face, \u8220\'93Its so rare to find an actual gentleman in Sin City. I\u8217\'92m pleased to have finally met one.\u8221\'94 She inclined her head to Marcus. \u8220\'93I\u8217\'92d make a similar comment to Cassie\u8217\'92s, but seems she\u8217\'92s already called dibs and it\u8217\'92s sisters before misters in my book.\u8221\'94 She winked at the fox girl.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Marcus covered his face with both hands. It was going to be a long Tutorial.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Oh, don\u8217\'92t stop on my account,\u8221\'94 Cassie\u8217\'92s grin somehow got wider. \u8220\'93I don\u8217\'92t mind sharing.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Yep, a very long Tutorial.}
